contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionary}} '''Beamish''' can refer to: Places: *[[Beamish, County Durham]], a village in England **[[Beamish Museum]] near Beamish *[[Beamish and Crawford]] a brewery in Cork, Ireland that produces the brand Beamish Stout.
